org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.decode

Class DecoderDummycode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.decode.Decoder
      • org.apache.sysds.runtime.transform.decode.DecoderDummycode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable

    public class DecoderDummycode
extends Decoder
    Simple atomic decoder for dummycoded columns. This decoder builds internally inverted column mappings from the given frame meta data.
    See Also:
